result.name: Bistecca Italian Steak House

reviews.text: Service was attentive and food was delicious. The steak came with a lot of flavour but I would have preferred it to be unsalted. I read on the menu that it came salted and I forgot to tell them to skip the salt. Mistake on my part. I would like to come back and try the home made Italian pasta!

I went for the lunch buffet. Excellent value. Extremely delicious food with good variety for their lunch buffet. Excellent service. Please be aware that this place is really small and it's like a power lunch place so it's super crowded at all times. And very loud.
Great , authentic Italian food.  Staff is superb and provide good recommendations. The cuts are large so great for sharing. Bring a little bit of Italy to Hong Kong.

This place was so great, that we ended up coming twice. The steaks are of course the highlight: very well done, tender, and tasty. The other dishes are great as well, I tried the meatballs and soup, and were all great. Also the bread they give at the start is amazing, as well as the free Limoncello they serve at the end.

Super highly recommended!

4 people. Got the sirloin steak. Marmoration was very good.
Even the fat was tasty which rarely happens.
The wine pairing was good and the service friendly and pleasant. Would recommend especially for business dinners due to location!

reviews.text: Really cool place. Trending and modern. Urban culture. Variety. Nightlife. Bars and clubs. Beautiful people. Crazy dressed people. Everyone as he likes. I really enjoyed walking through this neighborhood and soaking up the energy. That gives impressions of which one can still feed for a long time. Very inspiring. Very recommendable.

7-11 is the landmark of Lan Kwai Fong
I saw mamy people just buy drinks there when they feel drunk a little bit just get in to the club for dance 💃🕺 tonight I get in to Graffiti club

🍷today is Saturday ladies entrance for free but man pay 100$ that 100$ will be the coupon for drink in side   only beer   choose only one drink (beer only) and they will take your coupon

They play old songs here (we will rock you,I love it,Rude.. ) i was stay there just only 20 minutes

you will have a great time if you like crowds and the night goers. you can pop into a bar or grab drinks from 7-11 and hang out in the street. be careful as the sun will be rising before you know it. 

unfortunately broke phone the night of so I lost my photos to share
Cool street lined up with bars. Not a fan of the men grabbing my friend and me to get us to go into their bars. Beware of false deals that they’ll say to get you to go inside.

Safe and fun. 
The cocktail here taste good and people do dance.
